266
00:15:19,538 --> 00:15:20,211
Wait.

267
00:15:20,714 --> 00:15:22,968
Was she practicing a new seduction technique?

268
00:15:23,736 --> 00:15:25,334
That was impressive.

269
00:15:35,668 --> 00:15:37,210
Before school started back up,

270
00:15:37,246 --> 00:15:40,448
we were all spending the last
days of summer doing our own thing.

271
00:15:43,621 --> 00:15:44,537
How's your mom?

272
00:15:44,788 --> 00:15:46,293
You two getting along okay?

273
