A summer festival?

282
00:16:14,054 --> 00:16:15,513
The last day of summer vacation!

283
00:16:15,538 --> 00:16:18,011
Let's hang out and have some
mindless fun! What do you say?

284
00:16:21,490 --> 00:16:22,195
I thank you.

285
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,444
Uh, thanks for the sushi.

286
00:16:25,621 --> 00:16:27,416
Whoa. You're already finished?

287
00:16:27,623 --> 00:16:29,108
Sorry. I gotta get going.

288
00:16:30,357 --> 00:16:33,311
See ya! Let's do this again sometime. Take care!

289
00:16:38,396 --> 00:16:40,438
He's cheered up since last I saw him.

290
00:16:42,163 --> 00:16:42,719
Huh.

291
00:16:43,121 --> 00:16:44,260
A summer festival?

292
00:16:44,777 --> 00:16:46,190
I just thought of it today!

293
00:16:46,245 --> 00:16:47,413
I asked the whole class,

294
00:16:47,496 --> 00:16:49,621
but almost everyone seems to have other plans.

295
00:16:49,705 --> 00:16:51,759
I'm starting to feel rejected.

296
00:16:52,394 --> 00:16:54,390
All right. I'll go.

297
00:16:55,136 --> 00:16:58,068
Eh. It's not like I was doing anything else, anyway.

298
00:16:59,929 --> 00:17:01,627
Festival, you say?

299
00:17:02,527 --> 00:17:05,568
I'm honored my target would think of inviting me.

300
00:17:06,035 --> 00:17:08,869
But I'm afraid I'm out of country on business.

301
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,830
Argh!

302
00:17:09,873 --> 00:17:11,636
I'll pick you up! It's no trouble!

303
00:17:11,661 --> 00:17:14,371
Please! Mr. Karasuma's in a meeting! You're my last hope!

304
00:17:14,455 --> 00:17:16,038
If you don't come, no one will be there!

305
00:17:16,121 --> 00:17:18,455
Don't be ridiculous. I'm working.

306
00:17:18,553 --> 00:17:19,391
Yes, yes.

307
00:17:19,416 --> 00:17:22,330
Well, feel free to pop by and kill me anytime.

308
00:17:22,742 --> 00:17:24,325
I will, thanks.

309
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:29,148
According to Karasuma,

310
00:17:30,093 --> 00:17:33,176
our young friend pulled off the secret move I taught him

311
00:17:33,205 --> 00:17:35,274
as though to the manner born.

312
00:17:36,288 --> 00:17:39,533
Indeed. Every country has its Natural.

313
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:42,822
It's rather a shame I couldn't bring him with me.

314
00:17:50,330 --> 00:17:51,919
From the day you were born,

315
00:17:52,705 --> 00:17:56,860
