00:19:45,580 --> 00:19:46,192
Yeah.

353
00:19:46,288 --> 00:19:49,577
Turns out assassination skills
come in handy in the everyday world.

354
00:19:49,817 --> 00:19:53,899
Like getting all the men in the Chamber of
Commerce tent to buy you drinks? I can see that.

