00:20:02,621 --> 00:20:04,942
Only one at first, but he branched out.

361
00:20:05,138 --> 00:20:09,163
Started setting up in the stalls that closed
early after they sold out of all their stuff.

362
00:20:09,238 --> 00:20:09,860
